Should be able to separately specify something as absolute activator or 
inhibitor or both.  Absolute activators need to be calculated in the limit 
as the concentration goes to infinity. 

I made the following changes to effectively eliminate absolute activators
for now:

diff -r1.5 absolute_activation_inhibition_generation_method.c
